---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer" lang="en">

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Disclaimer</h1>
  <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-8">Please read carefully before using this site.</p>
  <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
    <div class="card p-6"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">No Financial Advice</h3><p>All content is personal trading records and research analysis only. No investment advice or trading signals.</p></div>
    <div class="card p-6"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Paper Trading</h3><p>All trades shown are paper trades (virtual funds). Does not represent real trading results.</p></div>
    <div class="card p-6"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Investment Risk</h3><p>Cryptocurrency markets are highly volatile. Make decisions after fully understanding the risks.</p></div>
    <div class="card p-6"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Content Accuracy</h3><p>We strive for accuracy but cannot guarantee completeness or timeliness of data.</p></div>
    <div class="card p-6"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Affiliate Links</h3><p>Some links are affiliate links. See Affiliate Disclosure for details.</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>
